ole<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'this.name ? '</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">this</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>name<span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">1000</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> heaeun <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">new</span> <span class=\"token class-name\">Person</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'heaeun'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\nheaeun<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">getName</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token comment\">/* \n\tthis ?  Window {0: Window, window: Window, self: Window, document: document, \n\tname: '', location: Location, …} \n*/</span>\n\n<span class=\"token comment\">// this.name ? ''</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"중첩-함수-또는-콜백함수가-일반-함수로-호출되는-경우-함수-내부의-this가-전역-객체를-바인딩하는-문제를-해결하는-방법\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#%EC%A4%91%EC%B2%A9-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-%EB%98%90%EB%8A%94-%EC%BD%9C%EB%B0%B1%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%EA%B0%80-%EC%9D%BC%EB%B0%98-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98%EB%A1%9C-%ED%98%B8%EC%B6%9C%EB%90%98%EB%8A%94-%EA%B2%BD%EC%9A%B0-%ED%95%A8%EC%88%98-%EB%82%B4%EB%B6%80%EC%9D%98-this%EA%B0%80-%EC%A0%84%EC%97%AD-%EA%B0%9D%EC%B2%B4%EB%A5%BC-%